{"id":239933,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-深圳公民发起我是公民-我要立案活动/","date":"2012-07-14T12:45:55Z","modified":"2012-07-14T12:45:55Z","title":"维权网 | 深圳公民发起“我是公民 我要立案”活动（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1vHOKVLqmQw/UAFmsIs3rTI/AAAAAAAAJS0/wOrbGT-j3lA/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1vHOKVLqmQw/UAFmsIs3rTI/AAAAAAAAJS0/wOrbGT-j3lA/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"263\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>深圳公民前往法院要求立案</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日下午</span><span>，深圳公民陈书伟、肖青山等五人到深圳福田区法院立案被拒，本来打算到现场支持的深圳维权人士郭永丰被提前控制在家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>深圳公民孙阳兵、李子韩等六人再去深圳福田区法院立案同样被拒，公民孙阳兵还被法警推搡倒在地上。直到孙阳兵报警，法警的态度才有所好转。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>下午两点，陈书伟、肖青山等人走进深圳福田区法院要求对销售不合格食品的商家立案，由于立案法官看到诉状上写着“一人枉法，全家光荣”和要求体现广东省委书记汪洋的“狗官论”，所以拒绝立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为此双方发生激烈辩论</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>法官说：“你这是乱用诉权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈书伟：“你在剥夺我的诉权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>法官说：“你厚脸皮</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>李子韩：“你脸皮薄吗”？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>法官：“你们这样搞，影响我们工作”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>肖青山：“立案是我们的权利，你们不能剥夺”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>法院通知删减材料</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈书伟：“只听说要补交材料，没听说过让删减材料的”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>法官说</span><span> </span><span>“只要你删除这行字，我们就立案”，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈书伟说</span><span> </span><span>“只要不违法，我就要坚持</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据悉，深圳一年的行政诉讼案总共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>例左右，陈书伟一个人就占掉三分之一以上，但是胜诉的案子只在百分之十左右。为了鼓励公民拿起法律的武器维护自己的合法权益，陈书伟等深圳公民发起“我是公民</span><span> </span><span>我要立案”的活动，希望更多的人能参与进来争取我们的权利，并称这是“有声的抗议”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4101420462848303417?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/2919d117E59BBE00.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}